      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Chief Secretary's Office ¶ Melbourne ¶  ¶ 9. July ¶  ¶ 187 ¶ 4 ¶ Sir, ¶ I have the honor, by direction of the Chief Secretary, to request that you will be good enough to cause this Department to be fu...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">74.07.09</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Ware</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 4979, pp. 629, 630, unit 37, VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Circular letter sent, with the name of the appropriate department inserted,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to 9 Ministers and 16 heads of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>subsidiary<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>departments<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>within<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Chief Secretary’s Department.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">Chief Secretary's Office</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">Melbourne</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>9. July<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">187</seg>4</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">Sir,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor, by direction of the Chief Secretary, to request that you will be good enough to cause this Department to be furnished, at as early a date as possible, with the undermentioned information, for the purpose of being laid before the Legislative</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Council<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">in compliance with an</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Order<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">on the motion of</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Honble. W.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>A.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>C. A'Beckett M.L.C.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">I have the honor to be,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="formtext" style="color: #2F5496; ">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient Servant</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Thos. Webb Ware</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">A Return of the names of all persons employed as supernumeraries and non-classified clerks in the Government Botanist Department shewing salaries, date of appointment and office in which they are employed.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Government Botanist<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>For reply see M. to J. Francis,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>10<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>July 1874<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(in this edition as 74-07-10d).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
